      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but it feels like it's not really doing enough lately and i'm super stressed with exams. i was thinking about picking up some St. Johns Wort from the apothek to see if it helps boost my mood more? is it okay to take them together or is that gonna be a problem?",
